channel.title: iHaxx Server - Version 2.1.0 - Developers
channel.description:
[center][img]http://ihaxx.net/images/styles/ambient-lightingv4-gold/images/logo.png[/img][/center] Hello MoparScape, This is the iHaxx Server Developers thread here at MoparScape. Let me start by explaining a little bit about the website + server itself, iHaxx started out in 2007 not long after i started coding in 2006, The project became quite big as it hit up 5,000 Registrations in the first 2 months of launching the server. In 2008 i decided to close the website due to issues that was occuring in my life. Now in August 2010 i started to develop iHaxx Server - Version 2 now this is where i want our website to gain users again. Since august i've developed a fresh highscores from scratch, i'm re-writing out a message centre + black mark system ([url=http://m.ihaxx.net]this can be previewed by going here[/url]) to work with my new template and i'm also looking to make the whole server SQL Handled From drops to shops. Few Images; [CENTER][img]http://iHaxx.Net/Chat.png[/img] [img]http://iHaxx.Net/Offense.png[/img] [img]http://iHaxx.Net/Loading%20Bar.png[/img] [img]http://iHaxx.Net/Login%20Box.png[/img][/CENTER] I'll be adding more shortly. Our Staff; Diesel (Me) - Server Developer & WebSite Founder Bot - Server Administrator & Graphics The Positions Avalible At iHaxx; [2]Server Developer [1]Client Developer [5]Forum Moderators [2]Graphics Artists [i]I'm not looking to hire in-game moderator or administrators, the only staff members are those who develop and design for the server & website itself.[/i] If you are intrested in one of the above positions you may simply fill out this application form and send it in a reply Below.
[center]iHaxx Development Applications[/center] Name: Age & Date Of Birth: Gender: What is your time zone: Please explain a little bit about yourself: Do you have previous expirience in the use of vBulletin forums: Do you have previous expirience in coding Java: What previous servers have you helped in development and have they succeeded: How many servers have you worked for previously: Why did you leave / be dismissed from your last positions: How much dedication can be expected from yourself: Email Address (MSN):
[b] Or you can simply add my and fill out the application over msn messanger. My Email is Root@iHaxx.Net[/b] [i] Now i don't want no idiots adding my msn telling me they can help my server by being a moderator because to be quite honest you won't even recieve a reply.[/i] Thanks Everybody I look forward to your applications Diesel
